    height: 16px;"></span></small>
                                                        </a></p>
                                                                                                        <p>Allamah Baqir al-Majlisi: <span> صحيح    </span> - Mir‘at al ‘Uqul Fi Sharh Akhbar Al al Rasul (12/59)</p>
                                                                                                                                        
                                                <p>

